column5: Took the canoe out for some Last of the year Largies.  As the fall quickly moves in, we'll be moving on to different species.
very nice thanks for taking the time to share it.  Art
Thanks! I have fun doin' the video thing.  It's surprisingly rewarding.
well you certainly found them, nicely done
don't put the bass gear away yet the season is just getting heated up as the big ones are starting to put the feedbag on.......
Nice job man bunch of good fish for sure!
